Text.SourceString: The Queen always complains about the slime during our walks. She can't stand the sight of it.//<portrait=happy>I find it rather intriguing. The slime, I mean, not Mother.
Text.LocalizedString: The Queen always complains about the slime during our walks. She can't stand the sight of it.//<portrait=happy>I find it rather intriguing. The slime, I mean, not Mother.

Text.SourceString: Well, perhaps she is too. She is quite a peculiar lady.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, perhaps she is too. She is quite a peculiar lady.

Text.SourceString: I've heard of something called <Italic>mod</> on your land. Is it a close relative of this slime, I wonder?//<portrait=happy>Right, right! Mud.//Mud...mud...mud, got it!//Funny thing is, Mod is this real crabby fish I know.
Text.LocalizedString: I've heard of something called <Italic>mod</> on your land. Is it a close relative of this slime, I wonder?//<portrait=happy>Right, right! Mud.//Mud...mud...mud, got it!//Funny thing is, Mod is this real crabby fish I know.

Text.SourceString: Oh, if only we could sweep this slime off to the shoreline like we do with the land-dweller's ships.//<portrait=happy>Not towards your shore, <Italic>of course</>... He he!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, if only we could sweep this slime off to the shoreline like we do with the land-dweller's ships.//<portrait=happy>Not towards your shore, <Italic>of course</>... He he!

Text.SourceString: I've always wondered...what's it like to walk on land?//<portrait=normal>To feel solid ground beneath your feet?
Text.LocalizedString: I've always wondered...what's it like to walk on land?//<portrait=normal>To feel solid ground beneath your feet?

Text.SourceString: You , land-dwellers, have <Italic>fingers</> on your feet!//Is it true you can wriggle them about just like hand fingers? What a fun twist!
Text.LocalizedString: You , land-dwellers, have <Italic>fingers</> on your feet!//Is it true you can wriggle them about just like hand fingers? What a fun twist!

Text.SourceString: Mother always fusses about owning too many different outfits. She insists we don't need them.//<portrait=angry>But you know, sometimes it's not about need, it's about joy!//<portrait=normal><NPCName>Aunt Liang</> told me that that you land-dwellers switch up your clothes every season! How delightfully whimsical!
Text.LocalizedString: Mother always fusses about owning too many different outfits. She insists we don't need them.//<portrait=angry>But you know, sometimes it's not about need, it's about joy!//<portrait=normal><NPCName>Aunt Liang</> told me that that you land-dwellers switch up your clothes every season! How delightfully whimsical!

Text.SourceString: Mother thinks they change because they're weak, like if they don't, they'll just perish.//<portrait=annoyed>I'm not buying it, <Italic>no sir!</>//Land-dwellers know how to have a good time, that's why they're all about the wardrobe change-up.
Text.LocalizedString: Mother thinks they change because they're weak, like if they don't, they'll just perish.//<portrait=annoyed>I'm not buying it, <Italic>no sir!</>//Land-dwellers know how to have a good time, that's why they're all about the wardrobe change-up.

Text.SourceString: Just a quick one, may I poke your arm? Is it the same as mine to touch?//<portrait=normal>The curiosity, oh, it's eating me up!
Text.LocalizedString: Just a quick one, may I poke your arm? Is it the same as mine to touch?//<portrait=normal>The curiosity, oh, it's eating me up!

Text.SourceString: A land-dweller in our halls! This day will be written in the shells, I'm telling you!
Text.LocalizedString: A land-dweller in our halls! This day will be written in the shells, I'm telling you!

Text.SourceString: You know, from a squinty distance, with your artificial tail...oh yes, you might pass for one of us!//<portrait=normal>Quite the sight to behold, you are.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, from a squinty distance, with your artificial tail...oh yes, you might pass for one of us!//<portrait=normal>Quite the sight to behold, you are.

Text.SourceString: I didn't find Father's verdict very just, if you ask me.//<portrait=normal>No, I simply couldn't stand by and let them cast you out into the cold, deep blue.
Text.LocalizedString: I didn't find Father's verdict very just, if you ask me.//<portrait=normal>No, I simply couldn't stand by and let them cast you out into the cold, deep blue.

Text.SourceString: I've got this little wish... That you'll show Mother not all land-dwellers are bad.//<portrait=normal>Maybe one day, she'll let me go up to the shore.//That would be so cool!
Text.LocalizedString: I've got this little wish... That you'll show Mother not all land-dwellers are bad.//<portrait=normal>Maybe one day, she'll let me go up to the shore.//That would be so cool!

Text.SourceString: I know you're meant to be here... I have this strong gut feeling about you.
Text.LocalizedString: I know you're meant to be here... I have this strong gut feeling about you.

Text.SourceString: Are you the curious type? Do you want a tour of the Kingdom?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you the curious type? Do you want a tour of the Kingdom?

Text.SourceString: You dress funny. I know... I know you need your goggles down here.//Still, it's funny-looking.
Text.LocalizedString: You dress funny. I know... I know you need your goggles down here.//Still, it's funny-looking.

Text.SourceString: Could I try it sometime, you think? That <Italic>thing</> on your mouth?
Text.LocalizedString: Could I try it sometime, you think? That <Italic>thing</> on your mouth?

Text.SourceString: It appears rather warm up there...on the shore, under the relentless sun.//<portrait=angry>You, describe to me how it feels.//<portrait=concerned>Umm...<Italic>please</>, if you'd be so kind...
Text.LocalizedString: It appears rather warm up there...on the shore, under the relentless sun.//<portrait=angry>You, describe to me how it feels.//<portrait=concerned>Umm...<Italic>please</>, if you'd be so kind...

Text.SourceString: I have this prized possession, a 'compass' if I'm not mistaken.//It's supposed to help with directions on land, isn't it? Such a wonder!//<portrait=annoyed>Do you know how to operate a 'compass'? Can you show me?
Text.LocalizedString: I have this prized possession, a 'compass' if I'm not mistaken.//It's supposed to help with directions on land, isn't it? Such a wonder!//<portrait=annoyed>Do you know how to operate a 'compass'? Can you show me?

Text.SourceString: I could spend all day listening to tales of the surface world.//<portrait=happy>Imagine, trees that lose leaves, buildings that touch the sky!
Text.LocalizedString: I could spend all day listening to tales of the surface world.//<portrait=happy>Imagine, trees that lose leaves, buildings that touch the sky!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s been keeping a vigilant eye on me ever since I was just a tiny little mermaid.//She's the only one Mother trusts enough to keep an eye on me.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s been keeping a vigilant eye on me ever since I was just a tiny little mermaid.//She's the only one Mother trusts enough to keep an eye on me.

Text.SourceString: I can see why...she's got a lot of them.
Text.LocalizedString: I can see why...she's got a lot of them.

Text.SourceString: The Queen is constantly trying to redirect my curiosity towards the ocean kingdoms, insisting I leave land-dweller wonders behind.//<portrait=annoyed>But, no! I believe there's much to learn from both worlds.
Text.LocalizedString: The Queen is constantly trying to redirect my curiosity towards the ocean kingdoms, insisting I leave land-dweller wonders behind.//<portrait=annoyed>But, no! I believe there's much to learn from both worlds.

Text.SourceString: Sure, sometimes I complain about Mother.//Despite this, I have no doubts about the love the Queen bears for me.//<portrait=normal>It may manifest in her ceaseless pursuit of my refinement, but it is love nonetheless.
Text.LocalizedString: Sure, sometimes I complain about Mother.//Despite this, I have no doubts about the love the Queen bears for me.//<portrait=normal>It may manifest in her ceaseless pursuit of my refinement, but it is love nonetheless.

Text.SourceString: I just took a walk with the King. I love telling him about my little adventures!//He calls me his spitting image and says I'm full of questions.
Text.LocalizedString: I just took a walk with the King. I love telling him about my little adventures!//He calls me his spitting image and says I'm full of questions.

Text.SourceString: On the other fin, my mother is all focused on turning me into the perfect queen.
Text.LocalizedString: On the other fin, my mother is all focused on turning me into the perfect queen.

Text.SourceString: I woke up feeling more energized than usual.
Text.LocalizedString: I woke up feeling more energized than usual.

Text.SourceString: Caught a whisper from my little fishy informants that you've been the hero of the hour, clearing up an area.//<portrait=happy>Thank you very much, <PlayerName>$Player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Caught a whisper from my little fishy informants that you've been the hero of the hour, clearing up an area.//<portrait=happy>Thank you very much, <PlayerName>$Player</>.

Text.SourceString: The currents feel a bit crisper than usual, and it's all down to you.//<portrait=happy>You should let <NpcName>Semeru</> know, ruffle his fins a bit! Hehe!
Text.LocalizedString: The currents feel a bit crisper than usual, and it's all down to you.//<portrait=happy>You should let <NpcName>Semeru</> know, ruffle his fins a bit! Hehe!

Text.SourceString: I want to go and explore so badly. I want to see if there are any new fish...or human trinkets.//<portrait=annoyed>I can just hear <Italic>her</> now, 'A princess doesn't swim off into unknown waters, Miraa...' Ugh.
Text.LocalizedString: I want to go and explore so badly. I want to see if there are any new fish...or human trinkets.//<portrait=annoyed>I can just hear <Italic>her</> now, 'A princess doesn't swim off into unknown waters, Miraa...' Ugh.

Text.SourceString: I'm going to ask the Queen if I can go exploring if I take Nagalita with me.//<portrait=angry>I don't want guards, they're so <Italic>lame</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm going to ask the Queen if I can go exploring if I take Nagalita with me.//<portrait=angry>I don't want guards, they're so <Italic>lame</>.

Text.SourceString: Maybe I'll just go alone, really quickly...a little peek wouldn't hurt, right?//Just a little peek.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I'll just go alone, really quickly...a little peek wouldn't hurt, right?//Just a little peek.

Text.SourceString: The water is remarkably clear today, I can almost feel the sun's warmth down here.//What a splendid day we have on our hands.
Text.LocalizedString: The water is remarkably clear today, I can almost feel the sun's warmth down here.//What a splendid day we have on our hands.

Text.SourceString: I apologize, but I'm simply unable to chat right now.//Off you go!
Text.LocalizedString: I apologize, but I'm simply unable to chat right now.//Off you go!

Text.SourceString: Greetings, <PlayerName>$Player</>! How are things doing up at the shore today?
Text.LocalizedString: Greetings, <PlayerName>$Player</>! How are things doing up at the shore today?

Text.SourceString: Well, hello there, land-dweller! I keep seeing you around, don't I?//Having a good swim so far?
Text.LocalizedString: Well, hello there, land-dweller! I keep seeing you around, don't I?//Having a good swim so far?

Text.SourceString: Let's resume our delightful conversations another time.//My fins need some rest.
Text.LocalizedString: Let's resume our delightful conversations another time.//My fins need some rest.

Text.SourceString: Mother always fusses about owning too many different outfits. She insists we don't need them.//<portrait=angry>But you know, sometimes it's not about need, it's about joy!//<portrait=normal><NPCName>Aunt Liang</> told me that that you land-dwellers switch up your clothes every season! How delightfully whimsical!

Text.SourceString: Greetings, <PlayerName>$Player</>! How are things doing up at the shore today?
Text.LocalizedString: Greetings, <PlayerName>$Player</>! How are things doing up at the shore today?

Text.SourceString: Well, hello there, land-dweller! I keep seeing you around, don't I?//Having a good swim so far?
Text.LocalizedString: Well, hello there, land-dweller! I keep seeing you around, don't I?//Having a good swim so far?

Text.SourceString: Let's resume our delightful conversations another time.//My fins need some rest.
Text.LocalizedString: Let's resume our delightful conversations another time.//My fins need some rest.

Text.SourceString: Oh, let's race to Sleepy Eel! Last one there has to sing the seaweed song!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, let's race to Sleepy Eel! Last one there has to sing the seaweed song!

Text.SourceString: You should see Putput during meal times. He waddles over like a tiny, grumpy king demanding his feast.//<portrait=normal>It's adorable and quite funny to watch.
Text.LocalizedString: You should see Putput during meal times. He waddles over like a tiny, grumpy king demanding his feast.//<portrait=normal>It's adorable and quite funny to watch.

Text.SourceString: I've had Putput since he was just a tiny bubble. He's grown so much.
Text.LocalizedString: I've had Putput since he was just a tiny bubble. He's grown so much.

Text.SourceString: It makes me kind of sad sometimes, thinking about how fast he's grown, because that means...never mind.
Text.LocalizedString: It makes me kind of sad sometimes, thinking about how fast he's grown, because that means...never mind.

Text.SourceString: Did I tell you about Nagalita's love for shiny things? She hoards anything that sparkles.//<portrait=normal>I once caught her trying to sneak a silver fork from the dining hall. She's such a curious little dragon.
Text.LocalizedString: Did I tell you about Nagalita's love for shiny things? She hoards anything that sparkles.//<portrait=normal>I once caught her trying to sneak a silver fork from the dining hall. She's such a curious little dragon.

Text.SourceString: The thought of someday not having Putput and Nagalita around...it terrifies me. They're not just pets, they're my babies.
Text.LocalizedString: The thought of someday not having Putput and Nagalita around...it terrifies me. They're not just pets, they're my babies.

Text.SourceString: Watching them grow older is bittersweet. I cherish every moment, but the fear of their eventual parting...it haunts me.
Text.LocalizedString: Watching them grow older is bittersweet. I cherish every moment, but the fear of their eventual parting...it haunts me.

Text.SourceString: One time, Nagalita mistook a shiny bubble for a gem and chased it all around the palace. It was hilarious watching her zigzag in excitement before it popped.
Text.LocalizedString: One time, Nagalita mistook a shiny bubble for a gem and chased it all around the palace. It was hilarious watching her zigzag in excitement before it popped.

Text.SourceString: Nagalita once saw her reflection in a shiny spoon and started flirting with it, thinking it was another tiny dragon.//<portrait=annoyed>I'm not quite sure about her age, but mating seems a bit premature. Why she would... ah, let's just leave it at that.
Text.LocalizedString: Nagalita once saw her reflection in a shiny spoon and started flirting with it, thinking it was another tiny dragon.//<portrait=annoyed>I'm not quite sure about her age, but mating seems a bit premature. Why she would... ah, let's just leave it at that.

Text.SourceString: I just adore dressing up Putput and Nagalita in miniature crowns and necklaces. They look like tiny royal dignitaries parading around the palace, don't you think?
Text.LocalizedString: I just adore dressing up Putput and Nagalita in miniature crowns and necklaces. They look like tiny royal dignitaries parading around the palace, don't you think?

Text.SourceString: You should see Putput with a tiny tiara; he puffs up with pride.//<portrait=annoyed>Or maybe it's just the weight of the jewels.
Text.LocalizedString: You should see Putput with a tiny tiara; he puffs up with pride.//<portrait=annoyed>Or maybe it's just the weight of the jewels.

Text.SourceString: It was one of Mother's old ones. She wasn't keen on me borrowing it for Putput. She can be so strict at times.
Text.LocalizedString: It was one of Mother's old ones. She wasn't keen on me borrowing it for Putput. She can be so strict at times.

Text.SourceString: Nagalita's crown used to be mine when I was younger. I've outgrown it now.//The sapphire adorning her crown is genuine, a relic from my great-grandfather, King Krakatoa himself.
Text.LocalizedString: Nagalita's crown used to be mine when I was younger. I've outgrown it now.//The sapphire adorning her crown is genuine, a relic from my great-grandfather, King Krakatoa himself.

Text.SourceString: Father's telling me not to venture into the deep sea without guards. It's <Italic>sooo</> annoying!
Text.LocalizedString: Father's telling me not to venture into the deep sea without guards. It's <Italic>sooo</> annoying!

Text.SourceString: No, I won't just float along with what's expected. There's a whole ocean out there to question.
Text.LocalizedString: No, I won't just float along with what's expected. There's a whole ocean out there to question.

Text.SourceString: I've been having this recurring dream, and it's the strangest thing.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been having this recurring dream, and it's the strangest thing.

Text.SourceString: In my dreams, I visit far-off lands and meet creatures of every shape and color. It's all so vivid.
Text.LocalizedString: In my dreams, I visit far-off lands and meet creatures of every shape and color. It's all so vivid.

Text.SourceString: Often, I close my eyes and picture myself strolling on land beneath a star-filled sky.
Text.LocalizedString: Often, I close my eyes and picture myself strolling on land beneath a star-filled sky.

Text.SourceString: Other times, I daydream about creating my own kingdom, a haven for royals who don't wish to be royals. Now, how exactly would that work, I wonder?
Text.LocalizedString: Other times, I daydream about creating my own kingdom, a haven for royals who don't wish to be royals. Now, how exactly would that work, I wonder?

Text.SourceString: I have this feeling in my scales that we're about to discover something amazing today. Trust me on this one.
Text.LocalizedString: I have this feeling in my scales that we're about to discover something amazing today. Trust me on this one.

Text.SourceString: Something tells me we should explore the northern caves today.
Text.LocalizedString: Something tells me we should explore the northern caves today.

Text.SourceString: I couldn't decide which keys to wear, so I brought all three. A princess must have options, right?
Text.LocalizedString: I couldn't decide which keys to wear, so I brought all three. A princess must have options, right?

Text.SourceString: Four keys? No, I've got three. The one at the end is my grandmother's hairpin. It's old, you know.
Text.LocalizedString: Four keys? No, I've got three. The one at the end is my grandmother's hairpin. It's old, you know.

Text.SourceString: Let's go on an adventure right now, no planning! Just you, me, and the open sea. Come on! Before the guards catch us.
Text.LocalizedString: Let's go on an adventure right now, no planning! Just you, me, and the open sea. Come on! Before the guards catch us.

Text.SourceString: Mother might get mad...yeah, you're right.
Text.LocalizedString: Mother might get mad...yeah, you're right.

Text.SourceString: I don't know why, but I feel like we should go to the surface today. Let's see where it leads us.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't know why, but I feel like we should go to the surface today. Let's see where it leads us.

Text.SourceString: If I sing to the sea creatures, do you think they'll sing back? In my heart, I believe they understand me.
Text.LocalizedString: If I sing to the sea creatures, do you think they'll sing back? In my heart, I believe they understand me.

Text.SourceString: Ugh, my kelp bed is too firm. I specifically asked for the softest sand from the Southern Tides.//They really must change this kelp immediately.
Text.LocalizedString: Ugh, my kelp bed is too firm. I specifically asked for the softest sand from the Southern Tides.//They really must change this kelp immediately.

Text.SourceString: Why have one course when you can have ten? That's how we do dinners at the palace.
Text.LocalizedString: Why have one course when you can have ten? That's how we do dinners at the palace.

Text.SourceString: Oh, it's a royal indulgence for sure! Each dish is a culinary adventure, one after the other. You must join us sometime.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, it's a royal indulgence for sure! Each dish is a culinary adventure, one after the other. You must join us sometime.

Special.SourceString: Ten courses? That sounds like a feast fit for a king! Or a princess, in this case.
Special.LocalizedString: Ten courses? That sounds like a feast fit for a king! Or a princess, in this case.

Text.SourceString: Well, it's not about eating it all, but savoring the variety! Each course is a small, delightful experience.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, it's not about eating it all, but savoring the variety! Each course is a small, delightful experience.

Special.SourceString: Wow, ten courses? How do you manage to eat that much?
Special.LocalizedString: Wow, ten courses? How do you manage to eat that much?

Text.SourceString: What's food waste?
Text.LocalizedString: What's food waste?

Special.SourceString: Doesn't that lead to a lot of wasted food?
Special.LocalizedString: Doesn't that lead to a lot of wasted food?

Text.SourceString: Have you ever seen those land-dwellers creations they call 'clocks'? I'm fascinated by how they mimic the rhythms of the tides.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you ever seen those land-dwellers creations they call 'clocks'? I'm fascinated by how they mimic the rhythms of the tides.

Text.SourceString: I wonder why land-dwellers build those enormous structures on land. Do they not dream of the freedom of the open sea?
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder why land-dwellers build those enormous structures on land. Do they not dream of the freedom of the open sea?

Text.SourceString: Guess what I discovered in a sunken ship, hidden among curious sea creatures? A key! Oh, I love keys. Can you guess which one is the land dwellers' key?
Text.LocalizedString: Guess what I discovered in a sunken ship, hidden among curious sea creatures? A key! Oh, I love keys. Can you guess which one is the land dwellers' key?

Text.SourceString: I couldn't resist; I had to take it.
Text.LocalizedString: I couldn't resist; I had to take it.

Text.SourceString: It's not easy being a princess, you know. But chatting with you always lightens my heart.
Text.LocalizedString: It's not easy being a princess, you know. But chatting with you always lightens my heart.

Text.SourceString: I love our kingdom, but there's a whole world above the waves calling my name. Don't you ever feel the same?
Text.LocalizedString: I love our kingdom, but there's a whole world above the waves calling my name. Don't you ever feel the same?

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I just blurt out what's in my heart. Thanks for listening and not judging, you're a true friend.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I just blurt out what's in my heart. Thanks for listening and not judging, you're a true friend.

Text.SourceString: Walking on land is trickier than I thought, but it's also kind of fun! Thanks for catching me when I fall, literally!
Text.LocalizedString: Walking on land is trickier than I thought, but it's also kind of fun! Thanks for catching me when I fall, literally!

Text.SourceString: Everything up there was so strange and wonderful! I'm like a little fish exploring a vast new ocean.
Text.LocalizedString: Everything up there was so strange and wonderful! I'm like a little fish exploring a vast new ocean.

Text.SourceString: I've been reminiscing about our time exploring your town. Do you recall the fish sign at that restaurant?//<portrait=normal>It was like a piece of home! It's funny how even up there, I found little reminders of the sea.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been reminiscing about our time exploring your town. Do you recall the fish sign at that restaurant?//<portrait=normal>It was like a piece of home! It's funny how even up there, I found little reminders of the sea.

Text.SourceString: I'm starting to get the hang of this 'land walking.' It's an adventure, and I'm glad you're there with me.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm starting to get the hang of this 'land walking.' It's an adventure, and I'm glad you're there with me.

Text.SourceString: Can you believe that coffee? My taste buds are still in shock!
Text.LocalizedString: Can you believe that coffee? My taste buds are still in shock!

Text.SourceString: I've never zoomed around so fast after drinking that coffee.//It felt like I had a dolphin's tail on land! Let's do that again, okay?
Text.LocalizedString: I've never zoomed around so fast after drinking that coffee.//It felt like I had a dolphin's tail on land! Let's do that again, okay?

Text.SourceString: Ah, the life on land is full of surprises!
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, the life on land is full of surprises!

Text.SourceString: Sitting with you at the dining table made me realize that adventures on land are exciting, but this, down here...it's not so bad after all.
Text.LocalizedString: Sitting with you at the dining table made me realize that adventures on land are exciting, but this, down here...it's not so bad after all.

Text.SourceString: Can you imagine me, a land-dweller? With legs permanently? The thought tickles my fins!
Text.LocalizedString: Can you imagine me, a land-dweller? With legs permanently? The thought tickles my fins!

Text.SourceString: I was only teasing about becoming a land-dweller, but part of me wonders what it would really be like. A princess with feet!
Text.LocalizedString: I was only teasing about becoming a land-dweller, but part of me wonders what it would really be like. A princess with feet!

Text.SourceString: My adventures on land with you have opened my eyes. There's a whole world out there, but the ocean will always be my first love.
Text.LocalizedString: My adventures on land with you have opened my eyes. There's a whole world out there, but the ocean will always be my first love.

Text.SourceString: Oh, I've been thinking about your door knob. I wasn't entirely joking that time at your grotto.//<portrait=happy>Someday, I might just add it to my collection. A keepsake from our time together on land.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, I've been thinking about your door knob. I wasn't entirely joking that time at your grotto.//<portrait=happy>Someday, I might just add it to my collection. A keepsake from our time together on land.

Text.SourceString: Dancing with you in the spotlight, I felt like a true star of the land. It's a night I'll always cherish in my heart.
Text.LocalizedString: Dancing with you in the spotlight, I felt like a true star of the land. It's a night I'll always cherish in my heart.

Text.SourceString: I never imagined I'd be swirling around a dance floor on legs. It was like living in a dream.
Text.LocalizedString: I never imagined I'd be swirling around a dance floor on legs. It was like living in a dream.

Text.SourceString: The moment we danced, everything else just faded away. It was just you and me, in our own little world. That was magical.
Text.LocalizedString: The moment we danced, everything else just faded away. It was just you and me, in our own little world. That was magical.

Text.SourceString: When I said I loved you out there on the dance floor, I meant every word. You've shown me a world beyond my wildest dreams.
Text.LocalizedString: When I said I loved you out there on the dance floor, I meant every word. You've shown me a world beyond my wildest dreams.

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$Player</>! You've floated into my day just at the right time. How are you?
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$Player</>! You've floated into my day just at the right time. How are you?

Text.SourceString: Oh, you're here! Darling, you always manage to bring a smile to my face.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, you're here! Darling, you always manage to bring a smile to my face.

Text.SourceString: Oh, hello <PlayerName>$Player</>! Glad you're here.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, hello <PlayerName>$Player</>! Glad you're here.

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$Player</>! I was just wondering what you were up to. It's like you read my mind!
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$Player</>! I was just wondering what you were up to. It's like you read my mind!

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, my favorite fish! I was hoping I'd see you today.
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, my favorite fish! I was hoping I'd see you today.

Text.SourceString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>! Just the person I wanted to see. How are you?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>! Just the person I wanted to see. How are you?

Text.SourceString: It's always so much fun exploring with you. I'm really glad we're friends.
Text.LocalizedString: It's always so much fun exploring with you. I'm really glad we're friends.

Text.SourceString: I always look forward to our adventures. It's nice having someone who understands my curiosity.
Text.LocalizedString: I always look forward to our adventures. It's nice having someone who understands my curiosity.

Text.SourceString: You're the best friend a mermaid princess could ask for. You make the surface world less intimidating.
Text.LocalizedString: You're the best friend a mermaid princess could ask for. You make the surface world less intimidating.

Text.SourceString: Do you ever feel like there's a special connection between us? More than just friendship?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you ever feel like there's a special connection between us? More than just friendship?

Text.SourceString: Lately, I find myself thinking about you even when we're not together. Is that strange?
Text.LocalizedString: Lately, I find myself thinking about you even when we're not together. Is that strange?

Text.SourceString: I get this fluttery feeling in my stomach whenever you're near. It's weird, but nice.
Text.LocalizedString: I get this fluttery feeling in my stomach whenever you're near. It's weird, but nice.

Text.SourceString: If I were a land-dweller, I'd definitely want to spend more time with you. Maybe even...as more than friends?
Text.LocalizedString: If I were a land-dweller, I'd definitely want to spend more time with you. Maybe even...as more than friends?

Text.SourceString: I wonder how it'd be to go on a real date with you. I bet it would be an unforgettable adventure.
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder how it'd be to go on a real date with you. I bet it would be an unforgettable adventure.

Text.SourceString: If I could, I would choose to spend every sunset and sunrise with you. Would you want that too?
Text.LocalizedString: If I could, I would choose to spend every sunset and sunrise with you. Would you want that too?

Text.SourceString: I had a dream last night about exploring the land. In it, you were holding my hand, and together, we walked across the beach.
Text.LocalizedString: I had a dream last night about exploring the land. In it, you were holding my hand, and together, we walked across the beach.

Text.SourceString: I miss you today.
Text.LocalizedString: I miss you today.

Text.SourceString: Have you heard of a TV? It's a box that shows pictures and tiny people.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you heard of a TV? It's a box that shows pictures and tiny people.

Text.SourceString: Windows to other worlds? That sounds magical! I wonder if they have any stories about the ocean.//<portrait=normal>I'd love to see how you land-dwellers view our underwater kingdom.
Text.LocalizedString: Windows to other worlds? That sounds magical! I wonder if they have any stories about the ocean.//<portrait=normal>I'd love to see how you land-dwellers view our underwater kingdom.

Special.SourceString: Yeah, TVs are quite common. They're like windows to different worlds and stories.
Special.LocalizedString: Yeah, TVs are quite common. They're like windows to different worlds and stories.

Text.SourceString: Learn and relax at the same time? That's impressive.//<portrait=normal>Maybe I could learn about your world's cultures and places without even getting my tail wet!
Text.LocalizedString: Learn and relax at the same time? That's impressive.//<portrait=normal>Maybe I could learn about your world's cultures and places without even getting my tail wet!

Special.SourceString: Sure, I've watched TV. It's a great way to relax and learn about things happening around the world.
Special.LocalizedString: Sure, I've watched TV. It's a great way to relax and learn about things happening around the world.

Text.SourceString: Live events? So it's like a portal to view things as they happen? How extraordinary!//<portrait=normal>I can't even begin to imagine all the wonders I could witness through this TV.
Text.LocalizedString: Live events? So it's like a portal to view things as they happen? How extraordinary!//<portrait=normal>I can't even begin to imagine all the wonders I could witness through this TV.

Special.SourceString: Yeah! TVs can show live events, movies, and even play music.
Special.LocalizedString: Yeah! TVs can show live events, movies, and even play music.

Text.SourceString: Really? It's so fascinating! Imagine a box filled with moving images and stories from the land.//<portrait=normal>It's like a magical window into your world. I'd love to see one someday
Text.LocalizedString: Really? It's so fascinating! Imagine a box filled with moving images and stories from the land.//<portrait=normal>It's like a magical window into your world. I'd love to see one someday

Text.SourceString: By the way, I never asked about your parents. Is your dad a king too?
Text.LocalizedString: By the way, I never asked about your parents. Is your dad a king too?

Text.SourceString: Really? That's incredible! We have so much in common then. It must be interesting to have a royal life above the water too.
Text.LocalizedString: Really? That's incredible! We have so much in common then. It must be interesting to have a royal life above the water too.

Special.SourceString: Yes, my dad is a king on the land.
Special.LocalizedString: Yes, my dad is a king on the land.

Text.SourceString: Ha! You're quite the joker. But seriously, I'm curious about your family.//<portrait=normal>They must be special to have raised someone like you.
Text.LocalizedString: Ha! You're quite the joker. But seriously, I'm curious about your family.//<portrait=normal>They must be special to have raised someone like you.

Text.SourceString: A king or not, a loving father is a treasure. I'd love to hear more about him.
Text.LocalizedString: A king or not, a loving father is a treasure. I'd love to hear more about him.

Special.SourceString: No, he's not a king, but I love him nonetheless.
Special.LocalizedString: No, he's not a king, but I love him nonetheless.

Text.SourceString: Of course, I didn't mean to pry. Let's talk about something more fun. Have you ever seen a dolphin dance under the moonlight?
Text.LocalizedString: Of course, I didn't mean to pry. Let's talk about something more fun. Have you ever seen a dolphin dance under the moonlight?

Special.SourceString: Can we talk about something else?
Special.LocalizedString: Can we talk about something else?

Text.SourceString: Have you ever seen a dolphin dance under the moonlight?
Text.LocalizedString: Have you ever seen a dolphin dance under the moonlight?

Text.SourceString: Isn't it just magical? It's one of my favorite sights in the ocean. Maybe next time, we could watch them together!
Text.LocalizedString: Isn't it just magical? It's one of my favorite sights in the ocean. Maybe next time, we could watch them together!

Text.SourceString: That sounds like a wonderful plan! It'll be a night to remember.
Text.LocalizedString: That sounds like a wonderful plan! It'll be a night to remember.

Special.SourceString: No, we can watch together sometime.
Special.LocalizedString: No, we can watch together sometime.

Text.SourceString: You remind me of my great-grandfather, King Krakatoa. May his soul rest in the depths.//<portrait=concerned>He wasn't much for fun either.
Text.LocalizedString: You remind me of my great-grandfather, King Krakatoa. May his soul rest in the depths.//<portrait=concerned>He wasn't much for fun either.

Text.SourceString: Can you fetch me some shade? The sun is lovely, but I need my comfort!//Or perhaps, a hat?
Text.LocalizedString: Can you fetch me some shade? The sun is lovely, but I need my comfort!//Or perhaps, a hat?

Text.SourceString: Oh, it's just perfect for a beach day, don't you think?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, it's just perfect for a beach day, don't you think?

Text.SourceString: Oh, this ticklish sand! It's so different from the smooth sands of my kingdom.//<portrait=annoyed>Is this why you land-dwellers always wear those little foot protectors? How peculiar!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, this ticklish sand! It's so different from the smooth sands of my kingdom.//<portrait=annoyed>Is this why you land-dwellers always wear those little foot protectors? How peculiar!

Text.SourceString: Do tell, is it always this warm under the sun? It feels kinda lovely on my scales.
Text.LocalizedString: Do tell, is it always this warm under the sun? It feels kinda lovely on my scales.

Text.SourceString: I've heard of beach games: the sand castle, volleyball...that's the thing over there, right?
Text.LocalizedString: I've heard of beach games: the sand castle, volleyball...that's the thing over there, right?

Text.SourceString: It feels weird that my hair isn't floating. It sticks to my skin...weird in a good way.
Text.LocalizedString: It feels weird that my hair isn't floating. It sticks to my skin...weird in a good way.

Text.SourceString: This breeze is lovely.
Text.LocalizedString: This breeze is lovely.

Text.SourceString: Oh, I saw this absolutely stunning girl at the beach, with the grandest hat I've ever seen! Such style and beauty.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, I saw this absolutely stunning girl at the beach, with the grandest hat I've ever seen! Such style and beauty.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Semeru</>! <NpcName>Semeru</>, where are you? You must find this girl at once! We have so many questions, and I simply must know more about her marvelous hat. Hurry!
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Semeru</>! <NpcName>Semeru</>, where are you? You must find this girl at once! We have so many questions, and I simply must know more about her marvelous hat. Hurry!

Text.SourceString: This inn is so cozy!
Text.LocalizedString: This inn is so cozy!

Text.SourceString: Where are <NpcName>Semeru</> and <NpcName>Denali</>? I'm craving some delicious curry.
Text.LocalizedString: Where are <NpcName>Semeru</> and <NpcName>Denali</>? I'm craving some delicious curry.

Text.SourceString: I'm still adjusting to these commoner chairs. They're so rigid!//Everything is so different from the floating rocks and seaweed back home.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm still adjusting to these commoner chairs. They're so rigid!//Everything is so different from the floating rocks and seaweed back home.

Text.SourceString: Everything here is so...dry. Do tell, should I put oil on my scales every day, or just on dry days?
Text.LocalizedString: Everything here is so...dry. Do tell, should I put oil on my scales every day, or just on dry days?

Text.SourceString: I noticed the owners of this lovely establishment are mirror spawns. Fascinating.//<portrait=normal>I’ve never met any mirror spawns in my life.
Text.LocalizedString: I noticed the owners of this lovely establishment are mirror spawns. Fascinating.//<portrait=normal>I’ve never met any mirror spawns in my life.

Text.SourceString: It's busy in here, isn't it? It's like a school of fish during feeding time.
Text.LocalizedString: It's busy in here, isn't it? It's like a school of fish during feeding time.

Text.SourceString: Duduuudubidam~
Text.LocalizedString: Duduuudubidam~

Text.SourceString: I'd love to go dancing. Maybe later, after a meal.
Text.LocalizedString: I'd love to go dancing. Maybe later, after a meal.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Semeru</> said that he requested the lights to be less dimmed. He thinks it's a hazard - for me!//<portrait=angry>Honestly, I'm a grown adult. He's no fun sometimes.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Semeru</> said that he requested the lights to be less dimmed. He thinks it's a hazard - for me!//<portrait=angry>Honestly, I'm a grown adult. He's no fun sometimes.

Text.SourceString: You can get such yummy foods here. It's quite delightful being human; you're not always bound to your chef's creations.//<portrait=happy>You can simply enter restaurants and, with a wave, demand they prepare you a feast!
Text.LocalizedString: You can get such yummy foods here. It's quite delightful being human; you're not always bound to your chef's creations.//<portrait=happy>You can simply enter restaurants and, with a wave, demand they prepare you a feast!

Text.SourceString: Be cautious with the wine, it can lead to a massive headache the next day. Not pleasant at all!
Text.LocalizedString: Be cautious with the wine, it can lead to a massive headache the next day. Not pleasant at all!

Text.SourceString: I'd be careful walking near the pool table. It appears someone has spilled their drink.
Text.LocalizedString: I'd be careful walking near the pool table. It appears someone has spilled their drink.

Text.SourceString: I suppose this is my home now, while I'm on land.
Text.LocalizedString: I suppose this is my home now, while I'm on land.

Text.SourceString: Hey there, <PlayerName>$Player</>! How goes the farm?
Text.LocalizedString: Hey there, <PlayerName>$Player</>! How goes the farm?

Text.SourceString: Oh, you look happy today! What's been going on?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, you look happy today! What's been going on?

Text.SourceString: Hey there, <PlayerName>$Player</>! Nice to see you again!
Text.LocalizedString: Hey there, <PlayerName>$Player</>! Nice to see you again!

Text.SourceString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>! I was just thinking about you. How are you?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>! I was just thinking about you. How are you?

Text.SourceString: Anything fun planned for today? Would it be okay if I tag along?
Text.LocalizedString: Anything fun planned for today? Would it be okay if I tag along?

Text.SourceString: Good morning, <PlayerName>$Player</>! It's always a treat to see you.
Text.LocalizedString: Good morning, <PlayerName>$Player</>! It's always a treat to see you.

Text.SourceString: Ugh, my throat feels weird. No more talking for me, okay? Everyone just be quiet for a bit.
Text.LocalizedString: Ugh, my throat feels weird. No more talking for me, okay? Everyone just be quiet for a bit.

Text.SourceString: I've decided I'm not talking anymore today. Off you go.
Text.LocalizedString: I've decided I'm not talking anymore today. Off you go.

Text.SourceString: My throat doesn't feel right...uhuk...uhuk.//<portrait=concerned>Maybe it's best if I keep quiet for a little while.
Text.LocalizedString: My throat doesn't feel right...uhuk...uhuk.//<portrait=concerned>Maybe it's best if I keep quiet for a little while.

Text.SourceString: The air is so fresh here. It feels different than being underwater – less... wet.
Text.LocalizedString: The air is so fresh here. It feels different than being underwater – less... wet.

Text.SourceString: I'm glad I decided to visit at this time of the year. Spring is gorgeous here.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm glad I decided to visit at this time of the year. Spring is gorgeous here.

Text.SourceString: Walking gets tiring. I don't know how you do it for so long.
Text.LocalizedString: Walking gets tiring. I don't know how you do it for so long.

Text.SourceString: The lake is my favorite place here...oh no, no, the beach...hmm...hold on...//<portrait=happy>Maybe the little garden near the healer's.
Text.LocalizedString: The lake is my favorite place here...oh no, no, the beach...hmm...hold on...//<portrait=happy>Maybe the little garden near the healer's.

Text.SourceString: I'm less slimy here. Here, feel it.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm less slimy here. Here, feel it.

Text.SourceString: I went to the museum earlier. They have such a massive body of water there – it made me want to swim!//<portrait=concerned>But <NpcName>Semeru</> said no.
Text.LocalizedString: I went to the museum earlier. They have such a massive body of water there – it made me want to swim!//<portrait=concerned>But <NpcName>Semeru</> said no.

Text.SourceString: Gosh, you caught me off guard!//<portrait=normal>What's on your mind?
Text.LocalizedString: Gosh, you caught me off guard!//<portrait=normal>What's on your mind?

Text.SourceString: I've noticed people sneezing quite a bit. Is that a spring ritual on land, or something in the air?
Text.LocalizedString: I've noticed people sneezing quite a bit. Is that a spring ritual on land, or something in the air?

Text.SourceString: Everything's blooming so beautifully! I saw some gorgeous red flowers this morning.//Of course, I didn’t pick them... I only take ones that have already fallen to the ground.
Text.LocalizedString: Everything's blooming so beautifully! I saw some gorgeous red flowers this morning.//Of course, I didn’t pick them... I only take ones that have already fallen to the ground.

Text.SourceString: The days are getting longer. It's nice, though I'm used to the constant ebb and flow of tides more than changing seasons.
Text.LocalizedString: The days are getting longer. It's nice, though I'm used to the constant ebb and flow of tides more than changing seasons.

Text.SourceString: I heard that the inn's owner is doing heavy cleaning. I'm not sure if I should leave the inn for the day or...
Text.LocalizedString: I heard that the inn's owner is doing heavy cleaning. I'm not sure if I should leave the inn for the day or...

Text.SourceString: I saw someone collecting a basket full of seashells at the beach the other day. That person must have a grotto project in the works.
Text.LocalizedString: I saw someone collecting a basket full of seashells at the beach the other day. That person must have a grotto project in the works.

Text.SourceString: I think <NpcName>Denali</> looks incredible in her attire. That shade of pink really suits her.
Text.LocalizedString: I think <NpcName>Denali</> looks incredible in her attire. That shade of pink really suits her.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Semeru</> needs to be more careful with his sandals. He almost slipped on them on the way up to the inn.//<portrait=annoyed>I keep saying. One step at a time, left, right...left, right...how hard can it be?
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Semeru</> needs to be more careful with his sandals. He almost slipped on them on the way up to the inn.//<portrait=annoyed>I keep saying. One step at a time, left, right...left, right...how hard can it be?

Text.SourceString: The potluck was a success yesterday, wasn't it?//<portrait=normal>Now, I'm not saying it's entirely because of our kingdom-grade seaweed, but I am suggesting that bringing the best seaweed in the ocean could have played a part.//<portrait=happy>There might be a connection there.
Text.LocalizedString: The potluck was a success yesterday, wasn't it?//<portrait=normal>Now, I'm not saying it's entirely because of our kingdom-grade seaweed, but I am suggesting that bringing the best seaweed in the ocean could have played a part.//<portrait=happy>There might be a connection there.

Text.SourceString: What time is the potluck tomorrow? It's at the lake, right?
Text.LocalizedString: What time is the potluck tomorrow? It's at the lake, right?

Text.SourceString: Are you done with your farming for the day?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you done with your farming for the day?

Text.SourceString: I overheard some humans are taking boats to a hill before summer arrives. That sounds like it could be a fun activity.
Text.LocalizedString: I overheard some humans are taking boats to a hill before summer arrives. That sounds like it could be a fun activity.

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, tell me – do I blend in well with your kind wearing this blue outfit?
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, tell me – do I blend in well with your kind wearing this blue outfit?

Text.SourceString: So, what do you plant when the heat rises like it is now?
Text.LocalizedString: So, what do you plant when the heat rises like it is now?

Text.SourceString: This warmth is glorious! You, <PlayerName>$Player</>, please find me the sunniest spot to bask in.
Text.LocalizedString: This warmth is glorious! You, <PlayerName>$Player</>, please find me the sunniest spot to bask in.

Text.SourceString: The heat is so delightful.
Text.LocalizedString: The heat is so delightful.

Text.SourceString: I expect nothing less than the freshest, juiciest fruits. Have them brought to me at once.//<portrait=surprised>Oh, sorry about that. I thought you're <NpcName>Semeru</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I expect nothing less than the freshest, juiciest fruits. Have them brought to me at once.//<portrait=surprised>Oh, sorry about that. I thought you're <NpcName>Semeru</>.

Text.SourceString: I've noticed there are more humans at the beach now.//You agree with me, <PlayerName>$Player</>, that warm weather must be drawing everyone out.
Text.LocalizedString: I've noticed there are more humans at the beach now.//You agree with me, <PlayerName>$Player</>, that warm weather must be drawing everyone out.

Text.SourceString: My scalp feels hot in this weather...is yours feeling the same way?
Text.LocalizedString: My scalp feels hot in this weather...is yours feeling the same way?

Text.SourceString: The town looks a bit different in Summer, but I can’t quite put my finger on what's changed.
Text.LocalizedString: The town looks a bit different in Summer, but I can’t quite put my finger on what's changed.

Text.SourceString: Next week is already Fall. The seasons change so quickly here!//I'm still not done with Summer.
Text.LocalizedString: Next week is already Fall. The seasons change so quickly here!//I'm still not done with Summer.

Text.SourceString: I'll be expecting you tomorrow at the beach cleanup, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//I'll be going without foot protectors. I don't want to risk a fall in front of everyone.
Text.LocalizedString: I'll be expecting you tomorrow at the beach cleanup, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//I'll be going without foot protectors. I don't want to risk a fall in front of everyone.

Text.SourceString: I'm feeling a bit tired from yesterday.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm feeling a bit tired from yesterday.

Text.SourceString: I think we'll head home tomorrow, rest underwater for a bit.
Text.LocalizedString: I think we'll head home tomorrow, rest underwater for a bit.

Text.SourceString: The Spooky Festival is tomorrow, right? Oh, wait...or is it in two days?//<portrait=normal>Hmm...I'll have to have <NpcName>Semeru</> check.
Text.LocalizedString: The Spooky Festival is tomorrow, right? Oh, wait...or is it in two days?//<portrait=normal>Hmm...I'll have to have <NpcName>Semeru</> check.

Text.SourceString: Oh, tomorrow is the Spooky Festival! Are you going to go in costume?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, tomorrow is the Spooky Festival! Are you going to go in costume?

Text.SourceString: We're here for the Spooky Festival on the 28th. Oh, so excited!
Text.LocalizedString: We're here for the Spooky Festival on the 28th. Oh, so excited!

Text.SourceString: Oh, the leaves are changing colors! How do they do that?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, the leaves are changing colors! How do they do that?

Text.SourceString: This crisp air is so different from the sea breezes I'm used to. It's refreshing.
Text.LocalizedString: This crisp air is so different from the sea breezes I'm used to. It's refreshing.

Text.SourceString: I went to the beach food establishment the other time, seeing all the commoners interact with each other.//<portrait=happy>Oh, one even asked me how I was doing. Can you believe that?
Text.LocalizedString: I went to the beach food establishment the other time, seeing all the commoners interact with each other.//<portrait=happy>Oh, one even asked me how I was doing. Can you believe that?

Text.SourceString: Oh, be careful where you step! My foot is right there.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, be careful where you step! My foot is right there.

Text.SourceString: I heard humans carve pumpkins in autumn. Fascinating!//I must try this pumpkin carving.
Text.LocalizedString: I heard humans carve pumpkins in autumn. Fascinating!//I must try this pumpkin carving.

Text.SourceString: The way these leaves crunch underfoot is oddly satisfying. Finally, a good use of feet.
Text.LocalizedString: The way these leaves crunch underfoot is oddly satisfying. Finally, a good use of feet.

Text.SourceString: I see people wearing scarves and hats. Do you think I should get one too?
Text.LocalizedString: I see people wearing scarves and hats. Do you think I should get one too?

Text.SourceString: I've tasted my first 'spiced latte' and possibly my last... I'm not a big fan.//<portrait=annoyed>Do you like it?
Text.LocalizedString: I've tasted my first 'spiced latte' and possibly my last... I'm not a big fan.//<portrait=annoyed>Do you like it?

Text.SourceString: It's quite chilly today, isn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: It's quite chilly today, isn't it?

Text.SourceString: Today's weather is just perfect.
Text.LocalizedString: Today's weather is just perfect.

Text.SourceString: I'm thinking of prolonging my stay a bit this time. Good idea, don't you think?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm thinking of prolonging my stay a bit this time. Good idea, don't you think?

Text.SourceString: I'm planning to tour some farms soon, and yours is first on my list. I'll have <NpcName>Denali</> get in touch with you to confirm.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm planning to tour some farms soon, and yours is first on my list. I'll have <NpcName>Denali</> get in touch with you to confirm.

Text.SourceString: Why aren't you out farming? Isn't that what farmers do?
Text.LocalizedString: Why aren't you out farming? Isn't that what farmers do?

Text.SourceString: I'm so excited for the fireworks show tomorrow!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm so excited for the fireworks show tomorrow!

Text.SourceString: Should I bring something for the host? I've heard it's traditional to offer gifts.
Text.LocalizedString: Should I bring something for the host? I've heard it's traditional to offer gifts.

Text.SourceString: The air feels exceptionally cold today.
Text.LocalizedString: The air feels exceptionally cold today.

Text.SourceString: I'm always fascinated by snow, no matter how many times I see it.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm always fascinated by snow, no matter how many times I see it.

Text.SourceString: I've noticed people, mostly <Italic>minnows</>, playing in the snow. Would it be odd if I joined in?//<portrait=normal>Maybe if <NpcName>Denali</> and <NpcName>Semeru</> play too, it wouldn't seem so strange.
Text.LocalizedString: I've noticed people, mostly <Italic>minnows</>, playing in the snow. Would it be odd if I joined in?//<portrait=normal>Maybe if <NpcName>Denali</> and <NpcName>Semeru</> play too, it wouldn't seem so strange.

Text.SourceString: I enjoy walking around the town when it's covered in snow.
Text.LocalizedString: I enjoy walking around the town when it's covered in snow.

Text.SourceString: What should I do today?
Text.LocalizedString: What should I do today?

Text.SourceString: Taking a break from farming, <PlayerName>$Player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Taking a break from farming, <PlayerName>$Player</>?

Text.SourceString: Taking a stroll, <PlayerName>$Player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Taking a stroll, <PlayerName>$Player</>?

Text.SourceString: What's on your agenda today, <PlayerName>$Player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: What's on your agenda today, <PlayerName>$Player</>?

Text.SourceString: Invite me to your cabin sometime.//I'd love to see how you live...once I manage to slip away from <NpcName>Semeru</> and <NpcName>Denali</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Invite me to your cabin sometime.//I'd love to see how you live...once I manage to slip away from <NpcName>Semeru</> and <NpcName>Denali</>.

Text.SourceString: Ah, <PlayerName>$Player</>! I miss you so much!
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, <PlayerName>$Player</>! I miss you so much!

Text.SourceString: I wish I could steal a kiss right now, but the guards are always watching.
Text.LocalizedString: I wish I could steal a kiss right now, but the guards are always watching.
